data.description: Come fall in love with this REMODELED residence in premium Surprise location!! The professionally re-done kitchen features on trend colored cabinetry, quartz counters, custom backsplash and high-end upgraded stainless steel appliances.  Enjoy those lovely Phoenix nights in the the recently updated backyard features large sparkling pool with water features.  Lots of turf area, large covered patio  and gas firepit. The extra large primary bedroom features separate flex space with double doors, great for office, den or exercise room.  The bathroom was recently redone with new tile surrounds, updated cabinetry, mirrors, lighting and more.  You will also enjoy the dual closets.  Additional upgrades include paint T/O, turf in front, garage cabinets, and more!! Make your appt now! The pristine main suite highlights a dedicated sitting room plus an immaculate ensuite w/dual sinks & a walk-in closet. The backyard is a private Oasis, boasting a sprawling covered patio, a fire pit, & a sparkling blue pool amidst the verdant greens. This gem won't disappoint you!
